intro.title: Welcome to Veloxx
intro.description: Veloxx is a lightning-fast, lightweight Rust library for in-memory data processing and analytics. It provides a modern, ergonomic API that competes with industry leaders like pandas and Polars while maintaining excellent performance and memory efficiency.
